{"title":"海岸上的仙人掌的颂歌","authors":["巴勃罗·聂鲁达"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海岸上的仙人掌的颂歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔智利〕　巴勃罗·聂鲁达"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的仙人掌，你有很多的刺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是砂石和旱风的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢的敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人祝贺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那顽强的健康，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的仙人掌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是在冬天看见了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凶恶的浓雾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啮咬着风吹雨打的悬岩；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨雷似的波浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袭击着智利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盐分推倒了雕像。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旷野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向破坏一切的大风暴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈服了，——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，平凡的英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰然地、平稳地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站在岩石中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有眼睛，没有叶子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有耳朵，没有神经。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是那样地坚定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头似的根子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧地抓住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球中的金属。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且，你庄严地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬起长满了刺的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正直的头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的头孤单单地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"露出在大地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着可怕的暴风的海洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来，在八月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们又遇见了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时，春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在睡眠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒冷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禁锢了整个海岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸上的一切"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛都是黑的；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波浪打着拍子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛是一条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿着丧服的大船；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都遇了险。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就在这时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天选中了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仙人掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你首先看见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的亲切的曙光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你那钢针似的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尖刺之间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一滴滴的血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诞生了鲜红的小花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出现了新的春天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海上，地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处都是春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切生存的东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切发出香气的东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切异常轻盈的东西，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切颤抖在柠檬树上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隐藏在壮丽的木兰中的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉睡的馨香中的东西，——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在等待着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的出现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干燥的沙滩上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只静静地站着的野兽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，仙人掌，被选作了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的报信的使者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而且很快地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当别的花还来不及"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开放的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的粗大的指头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神圣的指头的血红的蓓蕾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然开出了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇异的花儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出现了玫瑰色的花瓣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是你的故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是我的新的诗篇的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意义："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的姊妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然你们生活在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒原中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活在人们想奴役你的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你仍然顽强地工作吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不要屈服！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一天将要来到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了你，我的兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了你，我的姊妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也为了所有的人——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每个人的心中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将迸射出鲜红的光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一颗心都会开花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的兄弟我的姊妹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天没有忘记你们。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把真理告诉你们："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚强的仙人掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砂石的永不疲倦的儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"委托我把这些"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉一切愁苦的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不幸的心灵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要向自己，向你们再说一遍："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等着吧，我的兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等着吧，我的姊妹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我相信："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天会记着你们。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（孙玮译）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}